<PostParagraph>
    It's not exactly a fair fight–<i>The Vow</i>'s' trailer is a minute longer than <i>Seduced</i>'s–but there's clearly more lightness and color at the start of <i>The Vow</i>'s trailer (look at the buildup of green versus the fade-from-black in <i>Seduced</i>). There's also a lot more warmth–more deep reds and purples–compared to <i>Seduced</i>'s blues and grays. And even if they both boil down to something murky and gray, the average color of <i>The Vow</i>'s trailer is lighter than that of <i>Seduced</i>.
